Free State High School Administrators say problems with the way students dance at such events as homecoming and prom have prompted them to take some drastic measures.
Now if a student is caught dancing in a "provocative" way, they will be warned and then possibly kicked out of the dance.
Student council members have found a way to inform more students through a video (below) of their mascot showing what is and what is not appropriate.

i left my USB flash drive at Ohlone on tuesday night!
fuck!

im not worried that it's a 256mb flash drive, i'm not worried about the t-krew pics (i got em backed up), i'm not worried about the car pics (there will be other car meets)

im worried because all my pictures of alycia and me are on that damned flashdrive! that's all i got of pictures of us...damn

i used to have them backed up on my 128mb but i deleted the 128 and gave it to alycia.

god i hope someone in the computer lab found it and kept it in the lost and found.
shit...

i love alycia with all my heart and more.

yes that is all.
i got to spend a wonderful day with her in san francisco, went to safeway, trader joes, and walgreens.
watched the baseball game, hung around her apartment, hooked up her answering machine and new phone.

i miss her very much now, i hate leaving her apartment to go home.
worse part about seeing her is leaving makes me miss her more. 

anyway test tomorrow...must sleep early

Spent all day with Alycia even though I'm very tired.
It was very much worth it, gave her her big bowls, answering machine, cd's and letters.

Hung out at her apartment for a while and headed off shopping.

All-motor power comes from a 3SGE yanked out of a fifth generation Japan spec Celica with a slew of custom mods. The fully built power plant sports 86-mm forged pistons, HKS cams, adjustable cam gears and valve retainers. The OEM crank was lightened and balanced, and the head was ported and polished by DansToy. An individual throttle body setup and manifold was also created by DansToy, which looks great under the same hood as his custom high-rise header.

ahhhh deep forest...how i missed you.
i need some soothing music, delerium, enigma, deep forest, ect

i've been having this looming sense of gloom, like a knot in my stomach and the occasional sense of something isn't right.

i dont know what this is.

sometimes you just feel like pushing people away, separating yourself and just...leaving for a while...
doing stuff that isnt necessarly a good thing, but you just do it anyway...

just when you get to a point where you say "fuck it, this doesnt matter anymore"

i am at that point

yep sefl destructing is kind of fun once you get the fun of it.
sometimes its neccessary to hit rock bottom and go all the way back up.

October 4th...
Ingrid's birthday party. I have to remember that it's this saturday.

So yesterday was the NCC 1 year anniversary.

i got fucked up, i can't drink at all as rich, warren, my cousin, ect can tell you.
felt kind of bad because i was hella out of it, i wish i could have stayed awake to get into the talks warren, rich, my cousin and shit were having. I just remember giving hand signals and occasionally chiming in then slowly going back to sleep.

i arrived at 6, got messed up by like 11 and just curled up in a ball to sleep around 12. Woke up for a while until like 1 when i went to sleep and was woken up at like 2 when everyone went to denny's. Woke up at 5am sober and drove home.

sometimes i wonder if things would be alright if i just got what i've been waiting so long for...
a car, maybe i'm still trying to run away through driving, driving as fast and as hard as i can...

maybe it's a way to hide myself, close myself off some more rather then talk about my shit.
yeah my family is fucked up, yeah i miss alycia so much it hurts, yeah i miss being able to chill with people who are gone now, yeah....

gah!

i want new cologne but i have no moneys!!!
kenneth cole for men (not kenneth cole black but the regular one in the grey bottle)

smells so good...i want the 1.7oz... the 3.4oz is too big
maybe i'll buy some...or maybe i have to drag alycia with me like i did last time when i was looking for new cologne.

*sigh* memories...

yay....i found the full version of this song...
Sarah McLachlan - Fallen

w00t.
i love this song, something about her voice is so soothing and enthralling.

on other news, i miss alycia so much, i got to see her a little bit today.
She kept asking why I skip baseball games and stuff to see her, it's because alycia is one of the most important things in my life and i'd gladly drop baseball to spend time with her...whoa...how many guys would do that?!

kathy and i were on our way to the oakland game when alycia called me and told me they had to put her oldest cat to sleep, so I told Kathy I was going to go back So she decided to go home and watch the giants game rather then watch the B string A's. So I dropped her off and went to Alycia's for a while and made sure she was okay. Drove away and noticed my differential was making a little noise, I think I'm leaking differential fluid...maybe it's time for synthetic *grin*.

anyway went to fry's and bought alycia an answering machine so she can use her good phone instead of aki's phone which is very staticy. Also bought myself an emergency nokia cellphone charger incase i ever run out of battery because i'm sleeping overnight or something. It's about the size of my zippo and gives 60 minutes talk time or 60 hour stand by....awesome.

also went to ohlone's bookstore today to ask if my ipod had been shipped, i wont know till tomorrow!

spent most of tonight talking to alycia online and webcam whoring myself on alpha-q.net/jle/webcam

i miss alycia, she said my webcam is both a good thing and bad thing, she can see me but not touch me. Sadly I can't see her this week due to our bad planning and hectic schedules, but I'm sure when we do see each other it'll be great. I'm going to make sure I'm well rested.

Weekend...possible celica gt?! maybe...
Norcalcelica's party fo sho tho...

anywho....im listening to a cd i burnt for alycia now, i am one sappy bastard.
i've been sitting around talking to alycia all night, watching a few movies, listening to music and going through pictures...sentimental i am...

eventually...my post count will get smaller and i will quietly disapear, so don't mind me. i'm just chillin'
